title: List of Qatari football transfers summer 2012
text:
This is a list of <a href="Qatar">Qatari</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="transfer%20%28football%29">transfers</a> for the 2012 summer transfer window by club. Only transfers of clubs in the <a href="Qatar%20Stars%20League">Qatar Stars League</a> are included.
Players without a club may join one at any time, either during or in between transfer windows.
